    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu (Advanced Seal)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You send an advanced seal towards the target, which expands and wraps itself around them, leaving them @Condition[paralyzed]{paralyzed} and @Condition[blind]{blinded}, as well as causing them to suffer a -4 penalty to Listen checks. They can still speak. Removing the advanced seal is simple and can be done by anyone (the target, being paralyzed, cannot do so).</p>\n\n\n\n",
